### 1. Register with super admin email (auto-approved as super_admin)
POST http://localhost:4000/api/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{ "name": "Super Admin", "email": "solankinisarg815@example.com", "password": "Admin@1234" }

###

### 2. Duplicate super admin email registration
POST http://localhost:4000/api/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{ "name": "Super Admin", "email": "solankinisarg815@example.com", "password": "Admin@1234" }

###

### 3. Register a regular admin (pending)
POST http://localhost:4000/api/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{ "name": "Test Admin", "email": "testadmin@example.com", "password": "Test@1234" }

###

### 4. Try login as pending user
POST http://localhost:4000/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{ "email": "testadmin@example.com", "password": "Test@1234" }

###

### 5. Login as super admin — save token
POST http://localhost:4000/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{ "email": "solankinisarg815@example.com", "password": "Admin@1234" }

###

### 6. Get pending users (replace SUPER_ADMIN_TOKEN with token from step 5)
GET http://localhost:4000/api/v1/auth/pending-users
Authorization: Bearer SUPER_ADMIN_TOKEN

###

### 7. Approve pending user (replace SUPER_ADMIN_TOKEN and USER_ID)
POST http://localhost:4000/api/v1/auth/approve-user/USER_ID
Authorization: Bearer SUPER_ADMIN_TOKEN

###

### 8. Login as approved admin — save token
POST http://localhost:4000/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{ "email": "testadmin@example.com", "password": "Test@1234" }

###

### 9. Try to access beams with no permissions (replace ADMIN_TOKEN)
GET http://localhost:4000/api/v1/beams
Authorization: Bearer ADMIN_TOKEN

###

### 10. Set permissions for the admin (replace SUPER_ADMIN_TOKEN and USER_ID)
PUT http://localhost:4000/api/v1/permissions/USER_ID
Authorization: Bearer SUPER_ADMIN_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

[{ "module": "beams", "canView": true, "canCreate": true, "canEdit": true, "canDelete": false }]

###

### 11. Get permissions for the admin (replace SUPER_ADMIN_TOKEN and USER_ID)
GET http://localhost:4000/api/v1/permissions/USER_ID
Authorization: Bearer SUPER_ADMIN_TOKEN

###

### 12. Try beams again after permission grant (replace ADMIN_TOKEN)
GET http://localhost:4000/api/v1/beams
Authorization: Bearer ADMIN_TOKEN

###

### 13. Try to delete a beam — no delete permission (replace ADMIN_TOKEN)
DELETE http://localhost:4000/api/v1/beams/nonexistent-id
Authorization: Bearer ADMIN_TOKEN

###

### 14. Forgot password
POST http://localhost:4000/api/v1/auth/forgot-password
Content-Type: application/json

{ "email": "testadmin@example.com" }

###

### 15. Refresh token (uses httpOnly cookie set during login)
POST http://localhost:4000/api/v1/auth/refresh

###

### 16. Logout
POST http://localhost:4000/api/v1/auth/logout

###

### 17. Create firm (replace SUPER_ADMIN_TOKEN)
POST http://localhost:4000/api/v1/firms
Authorization: Bearer SUPER_ADMIN_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{ "firmName": "Sunrise Textiles", "firmCode": "SRT01", "challanEnable": false, "address": "Surat, Gujarat", "contactPerson": "Rajesh Shah", "contactNumber": "9876543210" }

###

### 18. List all firms — verify created firm appears (replace SUPER_ADMIN_TOKEN)
GET http://localhost:4000/api/v1/firms
Authorization: Bearer SUPER_ADMIN_TOKEN

###

### 18b. Search firms by name (replace SUPER_ADMIN_TOKEN)
GET http://localhost:4000/api/v1/firms?search=Sunrise
Authorization: Bearer SUPER_ADMIN_TOKEN

###

### 19. Get single firm (replace SUPER_ADMIN_TOKEN and FIRM_ID)
GET http://localhost:4000/api/v1/firms/FIRM_ID
Authorization: Bearer SUPER_ADMIN_TOKEN

###

### 20. Update firm — enable challan (replace SUPER_ADMIN_TOKEN and FIRM_ID)
PUT http://localhost:4000/api/v1/firms/FIRM_ID
Authorization: Bearer SUPER_ADMIN_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{ "challanEnable": true }

###

### 21. Delete firm (replace SUPER_ADMIN_TOKEN and FIRM_ID)
DELETE http://localhost:4000/api/v1/firms/FIRM_ID
Authorization: Bearer SUPER_ADMIN_TOKEN

###

### 22. Create mill (replace SUPER_ADMIN_TOKEN)
POST http://localhost:4000/api/v1/mills
Authorization: Bearer SUPER_ADMIN_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{ "millName": "Sunrise Mill", "millCode": "SRM01", "address": "Surat, Gujarat", "contactPerson": "Ravi Patel", "contactNumber": "9876543210" }

###

### 23. List all mills — test ?search= (replace SUPER_ADMIN_TOKEN)
GET http://localhost:4000/api/v1/mills?search=Sunrise
Authorization: Bearer SUPER_ADMIN_TOKEN

###

### 24. Get single mill (replace SUPER_ADMIN_TOKEN and MILL_ID)
GET http://localhost:4000/api/v1/mills/MILL_ID
Authorization: Bearer SUPER_ADMIN_TOKEN

###

### 25. Update mill name (replace SUPER_ADMIN_TOKEN and MILL_ID)
PUT http://localhost:4000/api/v1/mills/MILL_ID
Authorization: Bearer SUPER_ADMIN_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{ "millName": "Sunrise Mill Updated" }

###

### 26. Delete mill (replace SUPER_ADMIN_TOKEN and MILL_ID)
DELETE http://localhost:4000/api/v1/mills/MILL_ID
Authorization: Bearer SUPER_ADMIN_TOKEN
